board.name: te0728_1q
board.display_name: TE0728-*-1Q (512MB DDR). SPRT PCB: REV03, REV02, REV01.
board.description: Zynq-7000 Automotive TE0728-*-1Q (512MB DDR) Board (form factor 6x6cm) with 512Mbyte DDR3, two 100Mbit Ethernet, speed grade -1 and expanded temperature grade. Attention: MIO Bank1 Voltage Carrier Board depends. Please set correct PS Settings (default 3.3V). Supported PCB Revisions: REV03, REV02, REV01.
